{"id":110,"count":3,"description":"<h2>Mauritius<\/h2>\r\nIt is no surprise that Mauritius is described as \u2018heaven on earth\u2019, with its otherworldly beauty. This incredible island is renowned for its magnificent stretches of soft white sand beaches, sandwiched between the sparkling, turquoise Indian Ocean, and beautiful green cliff faces. If paradise is the goal, then Mauritius is surely it.\r\n<h3>Diverse Land &amp; Sea<\/h3>\r\nHowever, there\u2019s more to Mauritius than meets the eye. The island perfectly balances relaxation and luxury, with adventure and excitement. Hike to spectacular mountain viewpoints and waterfalls, and discover seven colored earth caused by past volcanic activity. Not only this, but also luscious plant life, and phenomenal snorkeling and diving. There is something unique about swimming off the shores of one of the most remote countries in the world. In doing so, discover the reef fringed lagoons, colorful corals, patterned fish, and magnificent sea turtles. Get ready to discover this exhilarating underwater world!\r\n<h3>Heavenly Nature<\/h3>\r\nMeanwhile, on land, nature is dense and luscious. Discover giant water lilies, beautiful tree-lined paths, the remarkable rolling green hills of tea plantations, and fresh papayas and pineapples. Gaze over green fields, while coconuts drop from the palm trees, giant tortoise graze nearby, and a rainbow breaks out over the dazzling ocean. There is no place on earth where such scenes exist, making it a world-class travel destination, and an undeniable \u2018heaven\u2019.","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/mauritius\/","name":"Mauritius","slug":"mauritius","taxonomy":"category","parent":0,"meta":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Mauritius Travel Guides &amp; Tips - Salt in our Hair Blog<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Mauritius It 